summary: Also known as Oshun (Osun, Ochun, Oxum). Associated with Yeye Kari (Mother of Riches), Iyalode (Queen of the Women), Laketi (She Who Responds), Yeye Osun (Mother Osun), Oore Yeye O (Kind Mother). Known as Yeye Kari (Mother of Riches). Symbolized by honey.
